      <div class="h20px"></div> 
      <div class="subcon_L"> 
       <p><font size="3"><font color="#ff0000"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US">“</span>走向北大<span lang="EN-US">”</span>俱乐部<span lang="EN-US">2013</span>年秋季（<span lang="EN-US">9</span>月）已经开始报名，先报先选座位，并且有礼品相送，每班限额，欲报从速！<span lang="EN-US">
            <u1:p></u1:p>
            <o:p></o:p></span></font></font></font></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">
         <o:p>
          &nbsp;
         </o:p></span></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="text-indent: -10.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20.6pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-line-height-alt: 8.7pt; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-para-margin-left: .98gd"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">
         <u1:p>
          <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>
         </u1:p>咨询电话：</span><strong><span style="font-family: 黑体; color: #339966; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">“走向北大”俱乐部<span lang="EN-US">2013</span>年秋季（<span lang="EN-US">9</span>月）语数课表</span></strong><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; color: #339966; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial">
         <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="text-indent: -10.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20.6pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-line-height-alt: 8.7pt; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-para-margin-left: .98gd"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; color: #339966; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><font color="#ff0000"><a href="http://www.tobdclub.com/show.asp?cid=27&amp;id=6437">http://www.tobdclub.com/show.asp?cid=27&amp;id=6437</a></font></span></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="text-indent: -10.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20.6pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-line-height-alt: 8.7pt; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-para-margin-left: .98gd"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>
         <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="text-indent: -10.35pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 20.65pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-line-height-alt: 8.7pt; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-para-margin-left: .98gd"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
         <u1:p></u1:p>
         <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">1</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">－<span lang="EN-US">3</span>年级教务长：<span lang="EN-US">18986051503</span>（魏老师） <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>
          <u1:p></u1:p></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">
          <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">4</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">年级教务长：<span lang="EN-US">13986026781</span>（郝老师） <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>
          <u1:p></u1:p></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">
          <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">5</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">年级教务长：<span lang="EN-US">15307135271 </span>（杨老师）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: red; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 楷体_GB2312">
          <u1:p></u1:p>
          <o:p></o:p></span></font></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">6</span><span style="line-height: 150%; color: blue; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">－<span lang="EN-US">9</span>年级教务长：<span lang="EN-US">13554013515</span>（郑老师）</span></font></p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">&nbsp;</p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">&nbsp;</p> 
       <p class="p0" style="line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">&nbsp;</p> 
       <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none"> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 36pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三升四（典）&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">任课老师：屈老师&nbsp;&nbsp;助教老师：曾老师&nbsp;&nbsp;13007138192</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">守株待兔之后</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">广埠屯小学四(4)班&nbsp;&nbsp;冯申钰</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一、愚蠢的人招人讽刺</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">自从守株待兔之后，那愚蠢的农夫只要走在路上就招人讽刺。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">二、人们讽刺那个农夫</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哎，哎，快看，快看，那就是幸运</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">捡到了一只兔子，然后一天到晚都在捡兔子的地方等，希望能再有兔子过来，结果不管粮草，在秋天就没有粮草的人，没想到还挺能撑的，撑到现在。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“是呀，是呀，那个人真够笨的。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三、愚蠢的人去借钱</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于是，听到了这些话的那个愚蠢的人去了他的姐夫家，问姐夫：“姐夫，我该怎么办？我没有吃的，没喝的！更重要的是我没钱，在山上摘野菜才挺到了现在，求您帮帮我吧！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“咔，好了，好了，你每天到我这儿来说这些理由，幸好，我有的是钱，要不然谁也救不了你，我就给你一百吧！”说完，他从口袋里掏出一百元的大钞，放在了那个愚蠢的人的手上。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“啊！谢谢姐夫，谢谢姐夫！”说完，他就跑回家了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于是，他在回家的路上买了一条新牛仔裤，又买了一件绿色的衬衣，又把剩下的钱拿去赌</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">博</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">了，最后钱全部用完了，他在家挺了两天不到，就连滚带爬去了姐夫家。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">哎，可怜的人，愚蠢的人，他为什么不知道节约用钱呢？</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“姐夫求求您行行好，再给我几百吧……”那愚蠢的人一边抱着他姐夫的大腿，一边一把鼻涕一把泪地说到。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哎呀，好吧，好吧，真拿你没辙，那我就大发慈悲给你两百吧！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“谢谢姐夫，谢谢姐夫！”那个愚蠢的人，一边亲着钱，一边走了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于是，他又去买了两件裤子，两件上衣，又去赌博，又去了网吧！结果，最后那两百块钱还是被那愚蠢的人“无情”“杀害”了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">哎，可怜的人，他又想去姐夫家要钱，可是，他一出家门，就看到一只兔子撞到木桩上，死了，于是，他赶紧跑过去，把兔子提起来，心想：又有便宜可占了。于是，他把兔子烤了，吃了，吃完了，他又去了姐夫家。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">四、愚蠢的人死了</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他一进姐夫家就呆了，原来姐夫家搬家了，他失望地走向大山，想去摘点野菜回家吃，可一看，傻了，野菜都没有了，什么都没有了，只剩下树，然后，那愚蠢的人回到家，向邻居借钱，可邻居不借，结果，挺了不到两天就死了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">哎，可怜的人，愚蠢的人，他为什么要不劳而获呢？</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">李白“对战”杜甫</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">武大附小（工学部）四(1)班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;路星宇</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"> </span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在2899年的一天，李白对杜甫说：“在2239年的一次比赛</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">中</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我没赢的了你，这一次我一定要把你PK下去。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头：一</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">到了第二天，李白在家心不安，在想：我可是诗仙，我不能输。李白想来想去也没出个战胜杜甫的法子来，于是，他就来到了考官家，问道：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">明天出什么题呀！告诉我好让我去琢磨琢磨，考官大人你看可以不</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我想了想便说：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">明天就考对诗句和作诗。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头二：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">到了第三天，李白和杜甫来到了我家，我说：“比赛开始，我们先考对诗句。”我</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">说的是上句</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">无边落木萧萧下，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">李白对下句：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不尽长江滚滚来。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我出上句：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一道残阳铺水中，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">杜甫对下句：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">半江瑟瑟半江红。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我说：“不错，一比一平，真不愧是诗仙和诗圣呀！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头三：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我把他们带到了庐山，让他们对景作诗，李白立刻作出了：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">望庐山瀑布</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（唐）李白</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">日照香炉生紫烟，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">遥看瀑布挂前川。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">飞流直下三千尺，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">疑是银河落九天。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我说：“李白你真牛，你把庐山之景写的很壮丽，真棒。”2比1，李白胜。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头四：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我把他们带到下雨时节，杜甫看到此景立刻作诗：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">春</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">夜喜雨</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（唐）杜甫</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">好雨知时节，当春乃发生。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">随风潜入夜，润物细无声。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">野径云俱黑，江船火独明。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">晓看红湿处，花重锦官城。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我说：“杜甫，你真棒，你把下雨时节写的很美丽。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我说：“诗仙，诗圣，你们写诗各有各的特点，不要埋没你的特点，要努力哦！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">杜甫和李白，你们一个是诗仙，一个是诗圣，你们各有各的特点，一个擅长写景，一个擅长抒情，所以你们两位都是赢家！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备来武汉</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水二小四（4）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;何博然</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">话说公元XXX年，刘备闲着无聊，便在军营里闲逛，却不小心步入了时空隧道，来到了2013年的武汉。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备刚到武汉，就看到天空中飞着大鸟（飞机），地上跑着各种奇形怪状的箱子（车）……刘备都看花眼了。待刘备反应过来，想：我人生地不熟的，要赶快找个军师（导游）啊。于是，刘备误打误撞，闯进了我家，向我说明了情况，我答应带他来个“武汉四日游”。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第一天：逛超市</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我带着刘备去了武汉本土超市：武商量贩。到了武商量贩里面，刘备好奇地左瞅瞅，右瞧瞧，还不停地问我问题。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这店里咋没有小二呀？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哈哈哈哈！这是超市，是我们自己选购要买的东西，如果有购物疑问，可以问导购员。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“那头顶的太阳是啥呀？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哈哈哈！那是电灯，靠电来发光，为人们照明。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这东西是何方神圣？”刘备指着冰箱问。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这不是神，也不是圣！这是冰箱！用来帮人们冷藏食品的。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">最后，我给刘备买了牙刷，毛巾等生活必需品，就回家了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第二天：坐地铁</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第二天，我带着刘备准备去</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">乘</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">坐地铁二号线到光谷广场。同样，刘备又问了我许多问题。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这一节</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">和</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">毛毛虫一样的箱子是什么？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“什么毛毛虫呀！这是地铁！今天我们要坐的！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“那这能上下移动的箱子是什么？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哦。咦，这跟楼梯一样，这不停动的又是啥呢？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“也是电梯，不过不是直达电梯，而是手扶电梯而已！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">向刘备介绍了这么多，晚上回到家早已筋疲力尽，刘备却还是精力充沛。希望明天不要这么累！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第三天：看电影</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">今天的行程是看电影，我们来到了银兴影城，选择了一部科幻片：《重返地球》。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“呀！是何人施了法术，把这么多人都困在这笼子里！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“小声点！这是电影，里面的人就像是画上的人一样，是真的！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“为什么要关那啥……灯呢？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“为电影看得更清楚呗！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“澎！”电影里朝我们开了一枪，刘备赶忙趴下。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“你趴下干嘛呀？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“他们不朝我开枪了么，我得躲呀！否则就被打伤了！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“什么呀！”我哭笑不得，“那都是假的！伤不到你！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哦。”刘备这才爬起来。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">看完了电影，我俩一边讨论影片的内容，一边走出影院，准备回家。回到家便美美地睡着了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第四天：散步</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">今天，是武汉四日游的最后一天，我要好好为刘备讲解一下！我们决定在武汉的街道上随便逛逛，了解一下武汉。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“那奇形怪状的箱子是什么喝？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“那是汽车。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“天空中飞的大鸟叫什么名字？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这是飞机，不是什么大鸟。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">走着走着，我们来到了省直机关二食堂。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备一看到“机关”二字，立马挡在我面前，还说道：“小心！有机关！千万别瞎走动！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我叹了口气，说道：“唉，机关是它的名字，不是那个机关！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备终于明白了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我们进去吃了顿饭，准备接着走。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">突然，“唰”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">地</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一响，我一看刘备不见了。这怎么办啊，导游把游客弄丢了，这导游也太失败了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我闷闷不乐地回到家后，一只信鸽飞到我桌前，我急忙拆下信一看，内容是这样的：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">何博然小军师：</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上次来武汉后，无奈误入时空隧道，不辞而别，深表歉意。然而本人认为武汉非常值得一游，于是明日，我将带着关羽和张飞再次前来游玩，还请你帮忙讲解！万分感谢！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">公元XXX年X月X日</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我的天啊！我一定要好好珍惜现在的生活，享受高科技的方便。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">诸葛亮来我家</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水一小四（1）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;陈香钰</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头一</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一天，我正在家里写暑假作业，突然，一只身上写着“563”的白鸽停在我家窗台上。我定睛一看，原来是只信鸽。于是，我把它脚上的信取下来，打开一看，原来是诸葛亮要到我家来参观！时间是明天上午9点！我兴奋地在家中这儿看看，那儿瞧瞧，看有哪些东西的位置不妥。家里被我收拾干净之后，我唯一的盼望就是明天上午9点的到来。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头二</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">第二天上午9点，诸葛亮先生一分不多，一秒不差来到我家。他一进我的家门，就忍不住东摸摸西碰碰。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头三</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不一会儿，他打开电冰箱，指着里面问我：“孩子，这是什么玩意儿？里面怎么还冒冷气？”我笑着回答：“诸葛亮叔叔，这是冰箱，您指的呢，是冰箱里的冷冻室，是存放饭菜的，所以会冒冷气啊！”“噢，原来是这样，真是好神奇啊！”诸葛亮先生恍然大悟。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不一会儿，诸葛亮先生的额头上就有了许多汗珠。也难怪，诸葛亮先生身穿这么多件衣服，家里又如此之闷，所以，我小心翼翼地问：“诸葛亮叔叔，您热不热？用不用开空调？”“什么什么？什么公掉？我怎么没听明白？”诸葛亮先生满脸疑惑地问。“诸葛亮叔叔，您说错啦！是空调，不是公掉！”“噢，原来如此，那就开吧！我从古代来，对现代的东西不熟悉，让我也感受一下现代高科技的好处吧！”“</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">OK</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">！”我答应了。我按了一下摇控器上的按扭！“嘀！”空调开了，诸葛亮先生兴奋地跑到空调底下吹风，我“见</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">情</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">况不妙”，赶紧说：“诸葛亮叔叔，不要对着空调吹，不然会生病的！”就我这句话，把诸葛亮先生吓个半死，“哎哟喂，吓死我了，原来好东西也有坏处，真是凡物都有两面性啊！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">镜头四</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“对了，我该回去了，再见！”“再见！”诸葛亮叔叔，有时间常来玩啊！我依依不舍地向诸葛亮先生道别……</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">哎！现代的机器真发达，古人来现代，可怜哟！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">回到战国&#x2014;&#x2014;在西施身边</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水一小四（2）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;王琦珊</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">穿越入战国</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有一天，我漫无目</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">地走在大街上，看见一幅画上画着一个美丽的女子。突然，狂风大作，一个好听的声音响了起来：“你回到了战国时期，我叫施夷光，人们都叫我西施。”我抬头一看，原来她就是有沉鱼落雁</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之美</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的西施。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">误把铜镜当碗</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施带我参观她的化妆间。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这个碗怎么能照出人的影子啊？”我指着一个棕色形状像碗的东西说。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施哭笑不得地解释说：“这是铜镜啊！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哦！”我恍然大悟，怪不得没有现代的玻璃镜好呢！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">同西施进宫</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">今天，经过我的再三肯求，西施终于同意带我进宫了！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“不过，你可要格外小心，举止大方、注意仪态哦！”在马车上，西施对我说。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我说：“放心吧！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">进了宫，我便四处张望。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“咦？这个又大又重像锅一样的东西是神马？”我好奇地问道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这个吗？它叫鼎。”西施笑着说道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“那为什么这个东西上面有三柱香？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施抿着嘴笑，说：“在我们这个年代，鼎是用来烧香拜佛的。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“原来是这样！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">去饭店吃饭</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我的肚子饿了，于是，西施带我来到了“蓝宇艳”饭店。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我们找了张桌子，还没等我坐下来，西施就说：“小二，上几个好菜！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我不解地问：“小二是什么玩意儿？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施掩着嘴笑，说：“小二就是上菜的人！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吃饱喝足，我们离开了饭店，来到了卖</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">首</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">饰的地方。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施给我买了一条闪闪发光的手链，很是漂亮。我们来到湖边。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在湖里划船</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一上船，我就对西施说：“这船也太老式了！还要用桨！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西施问：“那你们用什</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">么</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">划？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我强忍住笑，说：“用发动机，不用划！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">突然，一道强烈的金光刺得我睁不开眼睛，等我睁开眼时，已经坐在熟悉的小床上了。这不是梦！望着手上美丽的手链，我感</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">慨</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">万分：一定要好好珍惜现在的生活，古代多不方便啊！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备来到水果湖</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水一小四（5）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;王羽昕</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一、刘备厌烦古代生活</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备天天待在蜀国，已经闷得不耐烦了，就趁张飞、关羽等人不注意拿着金牌令箭悄悄地溜了出去</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">准备去看看城外的风景。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">二、刘备穿越到现代</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">可是他刚驾马来到一片树林的一角，还没一会儿，刘备的脚下居然出现了时空洞，他步入了时空洞，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">时空洞</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">把刘备带了进去，穿越到了2015年繁荣昌盛的水果湖。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三、刘备对水果湖充满疑问</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刘备看着满街道的人穿着一些奇怪的衣服和许多不认识的东西，就疑惑地自言自语道：“这是哪儿？”这时，十一岁的我路过这里，看到古代的刘备在这儿，吃了一惊，就问道：“你是刘备吧！咋来水果湖了咧！”刘备吃惊地说道：“啊！原来我穿越到了水果湖了啊！”说完，我就带着刘备在街上</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">溜达</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">起来。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">突然刘备指着“晨光”文具店问：“这是什么东西啊？怎么这么大啊！还有好稀奇古怪的东西咧！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“这是文具店，里面有各种各样的文具、书，我们在学习时是必须要用到的！”我自豪地介绍道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“哦！那可真稀奇！”忽然刘备停住了脚步，目不转睛地盯着马路看，还对我说：“那个是什么东西啊！黑漆漆的，是不是将黑白两界隔离分阶痕呢？还有那个白条条是不是刺客留下的暗号咧！需不需要我们帮你们除害呢？”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我大笑道：“哈哈哈！那不是分阶痕，而是马路；那白线是斑马线，是行人过马路的通道呀！”“哦！原来如此！”刘备捋捋胡须，说道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这时，一辆奥迪车从我和刘备的眼前驶过，刘备拍拍我的肩膀，奇怪地问：“刚才那庞然大物是什么呀？跑得那么快，还有一条灰色的尾巴呀！”我详细地解说道：“那</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">庞</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">然大物是汽车，一种交通工具，能载人的哟！而且那车牌还是公司大老板才能享受的奥迪喏！我告诉你，其实，不同的车都有各自相对应的牌子和型号。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“啊！真神奇！”刘备惊叹道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">过了一会儿，刘备对我说：“朋友，我想关羽、张飞他们见我不在蜀国，一定急坏了，你能送我回国吗？”我神气十足地说：“当然可以！”于是，我拿出现代科学家发明的时空穿梭机搜索到蜀国，对刘备按下确定键，骤然间，刘备就消失在茫茫人海之中了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">四、刘备回国的感悟</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">回到蜀国，刘备感叹道：时代在变化，我们古代人知多少啊！</span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
       </div> 
       <!--EndFragment--> 
       <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none"> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 36.855pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三升四（1）班</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">任课老师：张老师&nbsp;&nbsp;助教老师：田老师&nbsp;&nbsp;13027180219</span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 36.855pt">&nbsp;</p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《西游记》后传</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">华农附小四年级&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;吴昕熹</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“俺老孙回来了！”唐僧一行人取经归来，和老朋友热情拥抱，唐僧又念</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">叨</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">着很想大家，还说以后也带他们去西天取经。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">几个老朋友都说要听听他们的&#x2014;&#x2014;路途记，唐僧唠叨说在路上我们受苦了，要想听故事募捐些银子才行！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“我们可不能自费。”沙僧重复道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“孙大圣！我的东海龙宫风景优美，瓜果美味，来我这儿歇歇脚，吃穿不愁，再给我讲个故事就行了。”老龙王说道。唐僧一行人有了个落脚处，龙王不仅免费听到了故事，龙宫游人增多，门票越</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">涨</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">越高。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">玉帝来了说也想听听故事。八戒立马凑过来说：“要听故事可以，那得把嫦娥妹妹嫁给我才行！”玉帝想：我们家嫦娥那么漂亮，嫁给他多划不来呀！但我这么想听故事怎么办？算了！先把嫦娥送出去，过几天再让神把她接回来就行了。玉帝同意了八戒的要求，但他说：“只能把嫦娥借你三天，三天过了马上还我。”猪八戒想了想同意了。沙僧也赶紧说要玉帝赐流沙河给他养鱼，流沙河全让我管，里面所有的东西都得服从我的安排，不然别想听故事。玉帝无奈地点了点头。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王母娘娘也来了，吵着要听故事。孙悟空灵机一动说：“想听故事得过俺老孙这关。”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“你有什么要求？”王母问道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“只要你每天定时给俺老孙送桃子，保证以后不让我饿肚子就行！”孙悟空说。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“好吧！”王母娘娘长长叹了口气说道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">从此，师徒四人过上了衣食无忧的生活。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空的时空旅行</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水二小四（2）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;吕欣锐</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">话说西天取经回来之后，一日，孙悟空闲来无事，驾着筋斗云四处溜达，一不留神跌进了时空隧道，来到了2013年的武汉街头。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他抬头一看，眼前一栋房子上挂着一个大大的招牌&#x2014;&#x2014;“走向北大”，不禁心中奇怪了：这是个啥地方？待俺老孙前去打探打探。走进一看，只见一个个像镜子一样的东西正在播放《西游记》，孙悟空说：“这不正是俺老孙吗？嗯，奇怪了，师父、沙师弟、猪八戒怎么都困在这个小笼子里，这到底施了什么妖法，待俺老孙救你们出来。”只听“&#xfffd;&#xfffd;”地一声，显示屏里的师父、猪八戒、沙师弟不见了踪影，孙悟空正在纳闷的时候，走向北大的老师却跑过来揪住了他，人家把他当成了精神病。一番口舌之后，孙悟空只好变出一些银子，这才勉强脱了身。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空正要出去的时候看到一个长着红色头发，戴着墨镜的女人进来给孩子报名，孙悟空见状，大喝一声：“你是何方妖怪？”说完举起</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">金箍</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">棒，就朝女人打去，那个女人被打晕了，醒来以后那个女人要孙悟空赔钱，孙悟空见状心想：此地不宜久留，俺老孙还是回去和师父他们从长计议吧。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">欲知后事如何，且听下回分解。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空的时空旅行</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水二小四（3）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;周婧怡</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">话说唐僧师徒取经之后，孙悟空就回到了花果山管理它的猴子猴孙们。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有一天，孙悟空在山里散步，突然看见了一个大圆圈，孙悟空大叫：“这是什么东东，待俺老孙前去打探一下。”说完，孙悟空一个筋斗云，就到了武汉欢乐谷。孙悟空指着一艘船说：“这是什么东西！难道是妖怪设下的圈套？待俺老孙去坐坐。”孙悟空一跳，就跳上了海盗船；这时他看见了安全带，心想：这一定是妖怪用来绑我的绳子。只听“咔嚓”一声海盗船上的安全带就被孙悟空剪断了。过了一会儿，海盗船摇晃起来，孙悟空因为没系安全带，被海盗</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">船</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">甩了出去，一下子摔得鼻青脸肿。孙悟空心想：这个法宝真厉害，俺可要小心。于是孙悟空继续向前走着。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他来到了旋转木马跟前，孙悟空把它看成了真的马，跳上去就“驾”着赶马，可是马儿没有向前奔跑，而是忽上忽下晃动，一圈又一圈的，转得他头都晕了。孙悟空可不喜欢这玩意，赶紧跳了出去。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空在欢乐谷转悠了半天，每一个东西都令他很好奇，不可思议，他感叹道：“时代在进步，看来俺是落后了。”</span></p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
        <span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"> 
         <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none"> 
          <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三升四（2）班</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">任课老师：魏老师&nbsp;&nbsp;助教老师：秦老师&nbsp;&nbsp;13971205635</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融让梨新编</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">水一小四（5）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;董宇坤</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一天，孔融刚吃饱饭，正要上学时，突然，孔融的父亲叫住他：“孔融，给你一个梨吃吧！”“好。”孔融接过梨子上学去了。走在半路上准备吃梨时，他想，我刚刚吃饱早饭，有香肠、汉堡包、鸡爪、三明治……吃了那么多好吃的，我都吃不下这个梨了，把它让给别人吧！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">到了学校，孔融第一个看见的就是周杰伦，他平时爱玩游戏机，孔融说：“周杰伦，我让个梨给你吃吧！”周杰伦见孔融给他一个这么新鲜的梨，他刚想咬，却还犹豫了一会儿，心想：如果我吃了他的梨，他会不会让我把游戏机借给他玩呢</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于是周杰伦慢慢把手放下来，假装用手捂着肚子对孔融说道：“孔融，我肚子痛，不能吃梨。谢谢你的一番好意！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融心想：男孩不爱吃梨，那么女孩肯定爱吃。于是孔融来到走廊，向蔡依林跑去，说：“蔡依林，我这有一个梨，给你吃吧！”蔡依林看这梨又大又新鲜，刚想咬，却心想：如果我吃了他的梨，他就向我要我心爱的超级棒棒糖。于是慢慢地也把梨放下，然后蔡依林浅浅一笑说道：“孔融，我平时不吃梨，你还是自己吃吧！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这时，魏老师来了，孔融连忙跑过去说：“魏老师，我这有个梨让给您吃吧！”魏老师心想：孔融这小子平时不好好学习，快考试了就来让我把考试题目给他。“你这臭小子，平时不好好学习，快考试就来巴结我是不是？给我回去叫你家长来！”魏老师一脸严肃地说道。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融看着手中又大又新鲜的梨就很纳闷呢：怎么我想把一个新鲜的梨给让出去，都这么困难呢？</span></p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt">&nbsp;</p> 
          <span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"> 
           <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:  15.6pt none"> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三升四（3）班&nbsp;&nbsp;任课老师：魏老师&nbsp;&nbsp;助教老师：秦老师&nbsp;&nbsp;13971205635&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融让梨之后</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">中山路小学四（4）班&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;张留鲲</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">自从孔融让梨之后，东汉各大媒体报纸争相报道他尊老谦让的事迹。孔融一夜成名，被评为全国十佳道德模范之一，成为众家长教育孩子的好榜样。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融上小学后品学兼优，多次被评为“三好学生”。有一次还被评为“全国三好学生”，得到的奖品是当时非常稀有的ipad2。这时学习不好的宇泽跑过来对他说：“你能不能把</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">你</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的ipad让给我呀？”孔融爽快地答应了。宇泽拿着ipad蹦蹦跳跳地离开了教室。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融上中学后成绩依旧名列前茅，以优异的成绩考上了东汉科技大学少年班。他不仅学习好，还十分热爱运动，是一名体育健将。有一天他打篮球时不小心碰伤了头，在去医务室包扎的</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">路</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上，经过一棵石榴树时上面掉了下来的石榴正好砸到了他的伤口上，他一下子就昏了过去。等他醒来后一直在思考为什么石榴是往下掉而不是向上飞呢？为此他做了大量的研究，发现了“万有引力”定理，并把自己的论文寄给了他的笔友牛顿进行研讨。牛顿将这篇论文稍加改动，发表</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">了国际知名科学杂志上，引起了科学界的“大地震”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">牛顿也因此一举成名</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孔融大学毕业上班之后，工作踏实勤奋，赢得了公司上下的一致好评，被评为“全国先进工作者”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">东汉奖励他一辆宝马车。这可是东汉的紧俏商品啊！但</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不求名利，将宝马车转让给了从国外来东汉工作，急需一辆汽车却没有购车资格的同事雨方。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">就在他的事业如日中天的时候</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他突然患了重病。同学们纷纷到病房去看望他，有一位同事还带去了一大篮子他家乡的特产&#x2014;&#x2014;“山东大鸭梨”。孔融把大的梨子让给了病友们，留给了自己的依然是最小的那个，在场的人无不感动得泪流满面。这时只听孔融小声说道：“有些事压在我心里很久了。小学时我得的ipad是港版的，我之所以让给宇泽是因为我看不懂英文，“万有引力”的论文我本来是准备寄给专业</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">刊</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">物上发表的，却不小心装错了信封寄给了牛顿，我把宝马车让给雨方是因为我是色盲，分不清红绿灯，最后我想说我每次都拿最小的梨子是因为我的根本就不喜欢吃梨子……</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">听完孔融的这些话，他的同事和小伙伴们都惊呆了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">原来，我们的眼睛有时候也会欺骗我们啊！</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">西天取经之后</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">（★★）</span><span style="font-family: '黑体'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">武大二附小&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;舒新苗</span><span style="font-family: '楷体_GB2312'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">话说唐师徒四人经过了重重磨难，取得了真经，玉皇大帝给他们论功行赏，各自分配了仙位，孙悟空因为武功高强，负责天庭的治理工作，在去天门的时候，一不留神滑进了时空门……</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">过了N次之后，孙悟空睁开眼睛发现在自己前面有一栋房子上面写着：“西游网吧。”太奇怪了，这是什么地方？孙悟空心中满是疑问。走进一看，有一台镜子似的东西，闪着花花绿绿的图像，定眼一看，竟是唐僧</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">、</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">沙僧和八戒正在与人打斗。孙悟空气急败坏大叫道：“师傅，被何人施了妖法，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">困</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在这小小的笼子里，看俺老孙一棒。”只听“砰”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">地</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一声显示器坏了。师傅等人却不见踪影，悟空只好灰溜溜地逃走了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空走着走着，突然有一只大鸟从他头顶飞了过去，他觉得非常奇怪，就问旁边的小朋友：“你们这里的</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">鸟</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">好大呀！为什么会这么大？”那个小朋友</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">想</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">笑却又笑不出来：“叔叔，这是飞机，不是大鸟！”“哦！”</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙悟空刚回过神来，就看见了一个戴着五颜六色的头盔，骑着一匹怪模怪样的“铁马”的年轻少年，孙悟空定眼一看，便叫道：“何方怪，竟如此猖狂，吃俺老孙一棒！”说完，拿起金箍棒就打去。谁知“铁马”跑得飞快</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">“嗖”地一声没了踪影，孙悟空心想：此地不宜久留，还是</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">走</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">起为上策。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">只见一道闪电劈了下来，孙悟空醒来时已在天庭门口了。</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">欲知后事如何，且听下集分解。&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
            <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
              <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
           </div> 
           <!--EndFragment--></span> 
          <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
         </div> 
         <!--EndFragment--></span> 
        <p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">
          <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
       </div> 
